<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback Received - Thank You!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4ADE80;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feedback-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #4ADE80;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .priority-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .priority-high {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .priority-medium {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        .priority-normal {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #16a34a;
        }
        .response-time {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Statsor</div>
            <h1>Thank You for Your Feedback! üôè</h1>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong>{{user.name}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>We've received your feedback and truly appreciate you taking the time to help us improve Statsor. Your input is invaluable in making our platform better for all coaches and teams.</p>

        <div class="feedback-box">
            <h3>üìù Your Feedback:</h3>
            <p><em>"{{message}}"</em></p>
            
            <p><strong>Category:</strong> {{category}}</p>
            <p><strong>Priority:</strong> 
                <span class="priority-badge priority-{{priority}}">{{priority}}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="response-time">
            <h3>‚è∞ What Happens Next?</h3>
            <p><strong>Expected Response Time:</strong> {{responseTime}}</p>
            
            {{#if_eq priority "high"}}
                <p>üö® Your feedback has been marked as <strong>high priority</strong> and will be reviewed by our team immediately.</p>
            {{else}}
                <p>‚úÖ Your feedback has been added to our review queue and will be processed in order.</p>
            {{/if_eq}}
            
            <ul>
                <li>üìß We'll send you an email update when we've reviewed your feedback</li>
                <li>üîß If it's a bug report, we'll notify you when it's fixed</li>
                <li>üí° If it's a feature request, we'll keep you posted on development progress</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>In the meantime, feel free to continue using Statsor and don't hesitate to send us more feedback. We're constantly working to improve the platform based on user input like yours.</p>

        <h3>ü§ù Stay Connected:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>üì± Follow us on social media for updates</li>
            <li>üìß Check your email for our monthly newsletter</li>
            <li>üí¨ Join our community forum for tips and discussions</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Thank you again for being part of the Statsor community!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The Statsor Support Team</strong></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2025 Statsor. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Need immediate help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@statsor.com">support@statsor.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>